items.title: Trump admin. cuts grants for mental health, addiction treatment programs
items.description: The U.S. Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services Administration, SAMHSA, lost around $1.9 billion in federal grants, which were abruptly terminated...

items.title: "Fundamental" differences remain over Greenland's future, Denmark says after U.S. meeting
items.description: After the meeting, Denmark's foreign minister said they're eager to work with the U.S. while respecting the "red lines of the Kingdom of Denmark."

items.title: FBI searches home of Washington Post journalist for classified documents
items.description: The FBI's search is part of a probe into a federal employee suspected of mishandling classified information, Attorney General Pam Bondi said.

items.title: Trump says "killing in Iran is stopping," with "no plan for executions"
items.description: Potentially thousands have died from the crackdown to quash unrest amid protests.

items.title: U.S. says it's moving into next phase of Gaza peace plan, warns Hamas
items.description: Steve Witkoff said the U.S. expects Hamas to immediately return the final deceased hostage as part of its obligations under the deal.
